Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Franklin D Roosevelt and the New Deal
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydlyx
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 29 Jan 1982
The 100th anniversary of the birth of Franklin Delano Roosevelt, the origin of the New Deal, and FDR's political turnaround on the size of the welfare state.